      "instruction": "<p>Cut the<strong> remaining lemon</strong> into wedges</p><p>Set the <strong>smoky</strong> <strong>chicken & chorizo paella</strong> in the centre of the table, ready to share with the <strong>patatas bravas</strong>, <strong>garlic prawns</strong>, <strong>smoky chicken strips</strong>,<strong> garlic & herb olives</strong> and <strong>aioli </strong>in bowls – this is your <strong>tapas feast</strong></p><p>Sprinkle the<strong> remaining parsley </strong>over the paella and the patatas bravas</p><p>Garnish with the<strong> remaining</strong> <strong>lemon wedges</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
